title: Nidalee, Jarvan IV, Sejuani, or other
body: I am looking for a fun 3150/4800 ip jungler to play and possibly main.  I like both ap and ad and would like a champ who scales well into the late game and can have a good impact on the game.  If you think either what I have suggested or one of youe own choice suits this please comment below.

replies.body:
450: Yi
1350: Udyr
3150: Nidalee/Gragas
4800: Graves, Jarvan
6300: Elise, Ekko, Rek'sai

Nautilus
Malphite
Ekko

I dont know their prices though.
Maybe to be more precise, I dont bother to check their price
